Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么情况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高级酒店吗
